metadata.name: She was once a human
metadata.description: She was a human once. Others already considered her a soulless machine. After the accident, she had to undergo cybernization, now only her eyes remind her of what happened. I'm sure now no accident will harm her, because she is a machine herself. Now she is not a person, she is something more, her soul can be seen through her pupils and she is no different from ours.
